# Our Projects

> We’ve evaluated hundreds of high-impact, “what-if” ideas from federal employees, each aiming to improve how folks interact with the government. Here are some of the innovative current and past projects we have under our belt.

seo.title: 10x's Projects - Good for Government Tech | 10x.GSA.gov
seo.text: 10x's good-for-government, good-for-people projects make the world a little faster, smarter, better. Check out some of our projects.
